        Generates models from the database.
        Parameters:
        url - the database URL
        user - the user name
        password - the password
        schema - the schema to read from. null for all schemas.
        table - the table to model. null for all tables within schema.
        packageName - the package name of the model classes.
        folder - destination folder for model classes (package path not included)
        annotateSchema - includes the schema in the table model annotations
        trimStrings - automatically trim strings that exceed maxLength
        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException
